room_title: Escape room "Cartel: DEA Undercover" by 60out Escape Rooms in Los Angeles

room_description: You are undercover DEA agents in the middle of a special operation. You recently got word that the leader of the Juarez Cartel liked the product you sent him, and now he wants to meet up with you. The Juarez Cartel is known for their dangerous and brutal antics, so, if things start to go south, it may be too late.
